# UI Quality Standard — impeccable.style

Reference: https://impeccable.style/

> This project uses **raw Tailwind utility classes in a sky/blue palette**. daisyUI was removed — do NOT use `btn`/`card`/`badge`/semantic tokens (`bg-base-*`, `text-primary`) or `data-theme`.

## Core Principle

Every UI element must earn its place. Remove decoration that isn't information. If an element does nothing for comprehension or action, delete it.

## Visual Hierarchy
- One clear focal point per section. Never two competing headlines of equal weight.
- Strict 3-level type scale: display → heading → body.
- `font-display` (Sora 600–700) for h1/h2 only. Body is `font-sans` (Source Sans 3 400/600).
- Contrast drives hierarchy before size does.

## Whitespace
- Section rhythm: `py-16` minimum, `py-20`/`py-24` for hero/featured blocks.
- Card internal padding: `p-6` minimum.
- Stack with `gap-*`, not margin hacks.

## Color — raw Tailwind sky/blue

| Purpose | Classes |
|---------|---------|
| Brand / headings / accents | `text-sky-600` / `text-sky-700` / `text-sky-800` |
| Primary button | `bg-blue-500 text-white hover:bg-blue-600` |
| Accent / CTA button | `bg-sky-600 text-white hover:bg-sky-500` |
| Page background | `bg-white`, `bg-sky-50`, `bg-gradient-to-b from-sky-50 to-white` |
| Body text | `text-gray-800` / `text-gray-600` / `text-gray-700` |
| Success / error | `text-green-700 bg-green-50` / `text-red-700 bg-red-50` |
| Cards | `bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg` |

## Typography rules
```tsx
// heading
<h1 className="font-display font-bold text-sky-700">...</h1>
// body
<p className="font-sans text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">...</p>
```

## Spacing scale
Tailwind scale; prefer multiples of 4 (4 / 8 / 12 / 16 / 24 / 32 / 48 / 64).

## Interaction states
Every interactive element needs all four:
- Default
- Hover (`hover:`)
- Focus-visible — `focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-sky-500 focus-visible:outline-none`
- Disabled (`disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed`)

Never use bare `outline-none` / `focus:outline-none` without a replacement ring.

## Motion
```tsx
className="transition-transform duration-200 motion-reduce:transition-none"
```
Animate `transform`/`opacity` only. Never animate layout properties. Respect `prefers-reduced-motion`.

## Accessibility
- All images: meaningful `alt` or `alt=""` if decorative; prefer `next/image`
- Icon-only controls: `aria-label`; toggles: `aria-expanded`
- Color never the sole state indicator
- Min touch target 44×44px (`min-h-[44px] min-w-[44px]`)
- Keyboard focus must be visible

## Anti-patterns for this project
- Purple gradient heroes
- Glassmorphism (`backdrop-blur` + semi-transparent card bg)
- "Empower your journey" filler copy
- Identical icon-heading-text grid repeated in every section
- daisyUI classes / `data-theme` (removed)

## Layout container
```tsx
<div className="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
```
Never bare `container`.

## Quick checklist
- [ ] Raw Tailwind sky/blue palette (no daisyUI tokens)
- [ ] Hover + focus-visible ring on every interactive element
- [ ] `motion-reduce:transition-none` on transitions
- [ ] Headings `font-display`, body `font-sans`
- [ ] Container `max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4`
- [ ] `next/image` + `alt` for images
- [ ] No decorative element that doesn't serve comprehension or action
